- I set tmux prefix to ctrl-a
- split panes with prefix+% for vertical and prefix+" for horizontal
- copy mode with prefix+[
    - start copying with "v" and copy with "y"
    - use prefix+] to paste anywhere
- also copy using shift+mouse highlight and ctrl+shift+c
    - paste using shift+middle or just ctrl+shift+v
- prefix+z to toggle fullscreen
- alt+direction_key to switch between panes
- prefix+d to detach
- prefix+r to reload config
- prefix+ctrl+o to rotate clock-wise
